      <p>A <a href="ch72s22.html#MonstersT-Z159">yrthak</a> is blind. It senses sound and movement by means of a special organ on its long tongue. It emits powerfully focused beams of sound from the protrusion on its head. The creature is a yellowish-green color, with the wings and fin being more yellow and the head and body more green. The teeth are yellow.<a href="img/MonstersT-Z.Yrthak.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersT-Z.Yrthak.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch72s22.html#MonstersT-Z159">yrthak</a> is about 20 feet long, with a wingspan of 40 feet. It weighs about 5,000 pounds.</p>
      <p>Despite their intelligence, <a href="ch72s22.html#MonstersT-Z159">yrthaks</a> do not speak.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
